"      Patient information: Sex problems in men (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?20/42/21156?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Recovery after coronary artery bypass graft surgery (CABG) (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?26/53/27475?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Paraplegia and quadriplegia (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?16/20/16706?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Sex as you get older (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?35/45/36562?source=see_link\">",
